467
00:35:18,247 --> 00:35:20,468
This is South Medford, and as Ms.

468
00:35:20,488 --> 00:35:24,849
D'Antonio said, it's at the bus stop, which has now become

469
00:35:25,689 --> 00:35:26,950
practically obsolete.

470
00:35:27,390 --> 00:35:30,091
So we're talking about South Medford, not Medford Square.

471
00:35:30,672 --> 00:35:42,118
