00:37:13,802 --> 00:37:15,583
Anyone else would like to speak in opposition?

482
00:37:15,603 --> 00:37:23,928
Name and address for the record, please.

483
00:37:23,948 --> 00:37:24,308
Good evening.

484
00:37:24,328 --> 00:37:32,373
