00:39:21,324 --> 00:39:24,026
I would like to see the evidence if they can provide it.

510
00:39:28,173 --> 00:39:29,634
Currently they're open 6 a.m.

511
00:39:29,814 --> 00:39:30,714
and they want to go to one.

