00:39:48,202 --> 00:39:52,644
I've had cars there park 12, 15 days with no tickets on them.

517
00:39:54,665 --> 00:39:56,926
And also with respect to the business,

518
00:39:58,335 --> 00:40:10,298
some of the other residents have mentioned that this particular business is creating a monopoly in the area, and that can only be suppressed by rules and city council.

519
00:40:10,618 --> 00:40:10,938
Thank you.

