00:40:31,465 --> 00:40:38,311
Anne Fretz put the petition together, so I would like to read it here.

527
00:40:41,262 --> 00:40:55,646
So dear city council members, we the undersigned concerned residents are writing this petition to strongly oppose the proposed extension of the operating hours of Oasis restaurant to 1 a.m.

528
00:40:56,906 --> 00:40:58,447
I'm sorry, I'm a little anxious here.

529
00:41:01,048 --> 00:41:05,429
We are deeply concerned about the negative impacts such an extension would have in our community.

530
00:41:06,298 --> 00:41:14,604
public safety is our top priority, and we fear that the late night crowds and activities could increase the risk of crime and accidents in the area.

531
00:41:15,685 --> 00:41:26,393
Furthermore, late night noise disruptions have been a major issue for residents who live near the restaurant and those who home surround the public parking lot where Oasis customers park.

532
00:41:29,009 --> 00:41:31,452
The current operating hours until 11 p.m.

533
00:41:31,492 --> 00:41:36,117
are already causing disturbances during the late night, and an extension until 1 a.m.

534
00:41:36,137 --> 00:41:42,584
would only exacerbate the issue, with the disruptive activities in the parking lot continuing until 2 a.m.

535
00:41:43,705 --> 00:41:50,192
We believe that everyone has the right to a peaceful sleep, and that this extension would be a serious threat to our well-being.

536
00:41:51,162 --> 00:41:58,584
Additionally, both Oasis customers and staff have shown a constant disregard for the abutters and residents in the area for the past decade.

537
00:41:59,544 --> 00:42:04,765
And I can personally attest to that as a direct abutter of the restaurant and the parking lot.

538
00:42:07,186 --> 00:42:14,668
We have witnessed instances of Oasis patrons littering, parking violations, block driveways, trespassing,

539
00:42:15,279 --> 00:42:26,066
staggering public urination and exhibition of general disruptive behavior, such as blasting music, honking horns, screaming and drivers blocking roads close to midnight.

540
00:42:26,646 --> 00:42:32,510
This is unacceptable and has already caused considerable consternation and frustration for residents.

541
00:42:33,610 --> 00:42:39,272
We therefore urge you to reject the proposal to extend the operating hours of Oasis Restaurant 1 a.m.

542
00:42:40,072 --> 00:42:52,476
We believe that the negative impacts on public safety, noise disruptions, and residents' quality of life outweigh any potential benefits to Oasis owners and patrons by such a move.

543
00:42:53,157 --> 00:43:00,939
We ask that you prioritize the well-being and safety of residents in the South Medford community over the interests of the restaurant owners.

544
00:43:01,519 --> 00:43:03,180
Thank you for your attention to this matter.

545
00:43:03,644 --> 00:43:03,964
Thank you.

546
00:43:04,525 --> 00:43:05,966
Thank you, sir.

547
00:43:06,006 --> 00:43:07,667
Anyone else who would like to speak in opposition?

548
00:43:09,629 --> 00:43:12,351
And if I could just add something about like parking.

549
00:43:14,106 --> 00:43:30,276
If I work late and come home around 10 o'clock, I am unable to park in front of my own home, and I will have to circle my own neighborhood waiting for Oasis customers to exit, hoping that one of them is the patron who illegally parked in front of my home.

550
00:43:30,897 --> 00:43:40,242
If you extend this to 1 a.m., now I'm gonna have to go park at a great distance from my own home, and I'll be parking illegally in that instance as well.

551
00:43:41,323 --> 00:43:48,100
And I also have to say that there is a tremendous amount of food waste being dumped into that parking lot.

552
00:43:48,787 --> 00:43:51,349
Oftentimes they'll take food from Oasis, eat it.

553
00:43:52,049 --> 00:43:54,311
It often doesn't make its way into the barrel.

554
00:43:54,371 --> 00:43:55,311
It's on the street.

555
00:43:55,492 --> 00:44:01,756
I've got a dog that I have to worry about, but it has also dramatically increased the rodent population in South Medford.

556
00:44:03,697 --> 00:44:07,280
