561
00:44:22,648 --> 00:44:25,729
So the problems are only getting worse.

562
00:44:26,689 --> 00:44:29,391
So I truly urge you not to approve this.

563
00:44:30,351 --> 00:44:35,473
And I just really want you to consider that as residents, we have standing.

564
00:44:36,174 --> 00:44:41,196
So I've heard that you have to approve this,

565
00:44:42,068 --> 00:44:43,789
unless there is a compelling reason.

566
00:44:44,289 --> 00:44:50,091
Well, there is a compelling reason, and that is every resident in South Medford who stands opposed to this.

567
00:44:50,131 --> 00:44:51,912
So please do not approve this.

568
00:44:52,572 --> 00:44:52,972
Thank you.

569
00:44:53,432 --> 00:44:53,692
Thank you.

