00:44:56,513 --> 00:45:00,695
At this time, we're just gonna have people speak once at this time.

572
00:45:05,876 --> 00:45:11,961
They just need to raise their hand if they're on Zoom, so they can turn their camera on and wave, they can raise their hand, I'll see them.

573
00:45:11,981 --> 00:45:14,843
Name and address of the record, please.

574
00:45:15,024 --> 00:45:16,905
Lorenzo Puccio, Yale Street.

