00:45:44,793 --> 00:45:47,193
That permit that you're giving out is gonna be till 2 a.m.

583
00:45:48,514 --> 00:45:52,234
No one leaves at 1230 and they're out by one.

584
00:45:52,715 --> 00:45:53,355
It doesn't happen.

